the most horrible suffer.

362
00:19:17.704 --> 00:19:20.787
I'm Deputy Marshal Cruz.
This is Deputy Marshal Skinner.

363
00:19:20.870 --> 00:19:24.204
Um. it's not our place. but
in my time with Mr. LaChance.

364
00:19:24.287 --> 00:19:25.537
I couldn't help but notice

365
00:19:25.620 --> 00:19:27.120
