to make contact with.

367
00:19:28.787 --> 00:19:30.079
Mostly in Hawaii.

368
00:19:30.162 --> 00:19:31.495
California. too.

369
00:19:31.579 --> 00:19:32.787
Sounds like they're cooking up

370
00:19:32.870 --> 00:19:34.620
