371
00:19:34.704 --> 00:19:36.120
Thank you for sharing.

372
00:19:36.204 --> 00:19:37.787
Thanks for the memories.

373
00:19:37.870 --> 00:19:39.204
If you ever get to Oahu.

374
00:19:39.287 --> 00:19:40.662
I'm not there.

375
00:19:40.745 --> 00:19:42.495
God willing.

376
00:19:47.245 --> 00:19:48.829
Hard to defend
pointing the spear

377
00:19:48.912 --> 00:19:51.954
in this particular direction.
but...

378
00:19:52.037 --> 00:19:53.537
mission accomplished.

379
00:19:53.620 --> 00:19:55.829
Have either of you heard
from Kayce or Miles?

380
00:19:55.912 --> 00:19:57.787
Mm. wherever they are.
it's a better use of their time

381
00:19:57.870 --> 00:19:59.870
and skills
than what we just had to do.

382
00:20:06.995 --> 00:20:08.912
How we gonna get
this monster to talk?

383
00:20:08.995 --> 00:20:10.495
We've got no jurisdiction.

384
00:20:10.579 --> 00:20:13.079
By making him think
it's his best option.

385
00:20:13.162 --> 00:20:14.745
Is it ours. though?

386
00:20:14.829 --> 00:20:17.412
Cal only gave us his blessing
to talk to Hayley's mom.

387
00:20:17.495 --> 00:20:19.829
Sometimes you got
to break the rules

388
00:20:19.912 --> 00:20:21.204
for the right reasons.

389
00:20:24.162 --> 00:20:26.495
I'm not a marshal right now.

390
00:20:28.162 --> 00:20:30.204
I'm a dad
looking for his son's friend.

391
00:20:31.204 --> 00:20:33.495
If you want no part of this.
I respect that.

392
00:20:34.745 --> 00:20:37.037
You walk your path. not mine.

393
00:21:02.370 --> 00:21:03.870
You have a visitor.

394
00:21:06.412 --> 00:21:08.412
Chairman
must be looking for Kayce.

395
00:21:08.495 --> 00:21:10.412
Maybe he needs his help
with Hayley.

396
00:21:10.495 --> 00:21:13.870
Or he's pissed our boys are
stirring things up on his rez.

397
00:21:19.620 --> 00:21:22.370
Deputy Marshal Calvin.

398
00:21:23.453 --> 00:21:24.953
Apologies for the intrusion.

399
00:21:25.037 --> 00:21:26.370
No.

400
00:21:26.453 --> 00:21:27.870
It's no intrusion. Chairman.

401
00:21:27.953 --> 00:21:31.203
Though. uh. I am curious
what brings you here.

402
00:21:31.287 --> 00:21:33.328
What you've done for Kayce.

403
00:21:33.412 --> 00:21:35.578
giving him this new beginning.

404
00:21:35.662 --> 00:21:36.578
I thank you.

405
00:21:36.662 --> 00:21:38.412
Well. he's a true warrior.

406
00:21:38.495 --> 00:21:40.870
so. you know. there's
a self-serving element to it.

407
00:21:40.953 --> 00:21:43.578
Oh. the privilege
of leadership. huh?

408
00:21:43.662 --> 00:21:45.912
Every once in a while.
you can do something good.

409
00:21:45.995 --> 00:21:47.953
Indeed.

410
00:21:49.370 --> 00:21:52.287
Is there some good that
I could do for you. Chairman?

411
00:21:53.745 --> 00:21:56.912
This issue of missing children

412
00:21:56.995 --> 00:21:59.037
from the reservation has become
an epidemic

413
00:21:59.120 --> 00:22:00.828
for our people.

414
00:22:01.870 --> 00:22:04.245
And I'm sure it is hard
to combat with your...

415
00:22:04.328 --> 00:22:06.078
limited resources.

416
00:22:06.162 --> 00:22:09.537
The limit isn't just
our resources.

417
00:22:09.620 --> 00:22:11.620
but the will
of other law enforcement.

418
00:22:13.078 --> 00:22:15.745
Of all the indignities we face.

419
00:22:15.828 --> 00:22:17.787
few are as insulting

420
00:22:17.870 --> 00:22:19.953
as the indifference
to our lost children.

421
00:22:25.203 --> 00:22:28.203
Well. as a father. uh...

422
00:22:28.287 --> 00:22:31.203
I... I-I can only imagine

423
00:22:31.287 --> 00:22:33.162
the pain
of a child gone missing.

424
00:22:33.245 --> 00:22:35.828
A pain that's exacerbated

425
00:22:35.912 --> 00:22:38.662
when men with federal badges
get hopes up.

426
00:22:38.745 --> 00:22:41.953
Kayce and Miles were there
to just share some information.

427
00:22:42.037 --> 00:22:43.662
not make promises.

428
00:22:43.745 --> 00:22:46.828
Well. the promises are
only empty when not backed up

429
00:22:46.912 --> 00:22:48.203
from above.

430
00:22:53.203 --> 00:22:55.620
One of my most
challenging responsibilities

431
00:22:55.703 --> 00:22:59.245
as chairman is knowing
when to ask for help.

432
00:22:59.328 --> 00:23:02.162
Not something
men with power like to do.

433
00:23:02.245 --> 00:23:04.995
especially when it comes
to asking the very government

434
00:23:05.078 --> 00:23:06.745
that's waging a war

435
00:23:06.828 --> 00:23:09.162
on our way of life.

436
00:23:10.203 --> 00:23:12.120
You'd rather lose the battle
on your terms

437
00:23:12.203 --> 00:23:14.412
than win on someone else's.

438
00:23:15.620 --> 00:23:18.037
These girls deserve better

439
00:23:18.120 --> 00:23:20.578
than my pride
getting in the way.

440
00:23:20.662 --> 00:23:23.412
And I cannot lead the battle
to find them.

441
00:23:23.495 --> 00:23:25.578
so I'm here to ask

442
00:23:25.662 --> 00:23:26.828
if you will.

443
00:23:42.870 --> 00:23:43.787
Hey. this hole's taken.

444
00:23:43.870 --> 00:23:45.120
Go downstream.

445
00:23:45.203 --> 00:23:46.370
Thought you were
looking for company.

446
00:23:47.412 --> 00:23:48.662
Step off. bro.

447
00:23:48.745 --> 00:23:49.745
What the hell are you do...

448
00:23:54.620 --> 00:23:55.453
The hell. man?

449
00:23:57.370 --> 00:23:58.703
What kind of fish we catch?

450
00:23:58.787 --> 00:24:00.120
Think it's called
a "green_eyezz."

451
00:24:01.453 --> 00:24:03.412
Where are the girls you lured
off Broken Rock. Hayley and Ava?

452
00:24:03.495 --> 00:24:04.745
I don't know them.

453
00:24:04.828 --> 00:24:06.037
Wrong answer.

454
00:24:10.537 --> 00:24:12.870
I don't know
where Hayley or Ava's at!

455
00:24:12.953 --> 00:24:14.328
Suddenly remember their names.

456
00:24:14.412 --> 00:24:15.787
Couple of stalkers.

457
00:24:15.870 --> 00:24:17.245
Couldn't keep off my jock.

458
00:24:17.328 --> 00:24:18.787
This one's a fighter.

459
00:24:18.870 --> 00:24:20.078
Might have to see if our lures

460
00:24:20.162 --> 00:24:21.037
are strong enough.

461
00:24:21.120 --> 00:24:22.703
Okay.

462
00:24:22.787 --> 00:24:24.328
I just had some fun with 'em
and tossed 'em aside.

463
00:24:24.412 --> 00:24:25.495
No big deal.

464
00:24:25.578 --> 00:24:27.037
Using pictures and videos

465
00:24:27.120 --> 00:24:28.453
to blackmail them
into sex work's a little fun?!

466
00:24:31.870 --> 00:24:32.787
How many other girls?

467
00:24:34.537 --> 00:24:37.453
He's got dozens
of conversations going.

468
00:24:37.537 --> 00:24:39.078
Where are they?

469
00:24:40.162 --> 00:24:42.870
I will gut you right here
if you don't talk.

470
00:24:44.245 --> 00:24:46.703
If I tell you.
will you let me go?

471
00:24:50.787 --> 00:24:52.703
I won't hurt you.

472
00:24:55.578 --> 00:24:57.412
Hey.

473
00:24:57.495 --> 00:24:58.953
Gifford just gave his blessing.

474
00:24:59.037 --> 00:25:01.120
We can assist
the Broken Rock tribal police.

475
00:25:01.203 --> 00:25:05.037
Tactical Swiss Army knife gets
to help the most vulnerable.

476
00:25:05.120 --> 00:25:07.162
That's a good win.

477
00:25:07.245 --> 00:25:08.745
What's this?

478
00:25:08.828 --> 00:25:11.870
Y'all been working
this case behind my back?

479
00:25:11.953 --> 00:25:14.412
Kind of right
in front of you. actually.

480
00:25:14.495 --> 00:25:16.495
I'd consider this
a "beg for forgiveness"

481
00:25:16.578 --> 00:25:18.620
versus an "ask
for permission" situation.

482
00:25:18.703 --> 00:25:21.245
Okay.
What do you got?

483
00:25:21.328 --> 00:25:23.620
Okay. meet Kurt Bludsoe.
fully-formed POS.

484
00:25:23.703 --> 00:25:26.037
Long jacket filled with
pimping and pandering.

485
00:25:26.120 --> 00:25:27.703
I mean. add sex trafficking
to that résumé.

486
00:25:27.787 --> 00:25:29.245
he goes away for life.

487
00:25:29.328 --> 00:25:31.078
Kayce and Miles
think he's running

488
00:25:31.162 --> 00:25:32.328
Hayley and other girls.

489
00:25:32.412 --> 00:25:34.120
Got them from some lowlife

490
00:25:34.203 --> 00:25:35.787
who lured them off the rez.

491
00:25:35.870 --> 00:25:37.620
Let's get an interstate
BOLO out. We're gonna cast

492
00:25:37.703 --> 00:25:39.370
