I want you to forward

493
00:25:39.453 --> 00:25:41.703
that mug to state troopers
and local PD in the region.

494
00:25:41.787 --> 00:25:43.828
Okay. I'll dig up
a list of family. friends

495
00:25:43.912 --> 00:25:45.578
- and former cellies.
- Cool.

496
00:25:45.662 --> 00:25:46.912
And. hey. hey.

497
00:25:46.995 --> 00:25:48.787
Let Kayce and Miles know
we're on the job.

498
00:25:48.870 --> 00:25:49.953
They can come home.

499
00:26:13.912 --> 00:26:15.662
You said I wouldn't get hurt.

500
00:26:15.745 --> 00:26:17.745
I said I wouldn't hurt you.

501
00:26:27.828 --> 00:26:30.078
You preyed on the rez.

502
00:26:30.162 --> 00:26:32.162
now the rez
is gonna prey on you.

503
00:26:37.245 --> 00:26:40.162
Hey! Hey... No!

504
00:26:40.245 --> 00:26:43.120
No. no. no. please. no!
Let me go!

505
00:26:43.203 --> 00:26:45.037
No. I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

506
00:26:45.120 --> 00:26:47.037
I'm sorry!
Please. I...

507
00:26:47.120 --> 00:26:48.995
No. No! Let me go!

508
00:26:49.078 --> 00:26:51.078
No!

509
00:27:14.495 --> 00:27:15.662
You got in late.

510
00:27:18.245 --> 00:27:19.454
What's all this?

511
00:27:19.537 --> 00:27:22.287
Mom's stuff.

512
00:27:22.370 --> 00:27:23.829
Trying to find
something we can read

513
00:27:23.912 --> 00:27:25.245
for the ceremony.

514
00:27:27.829 --> 00:27:30.704
Well. I'll have to see
if I can go.

515
00:27:30.787 --> 00:27:32.954
Finding Hayley's
gonna take priority.

516
00:27:33.037 --> 00:27:34.329
Wait. what?

517
00:27:34.412 --> 00:27:36.245
So she is missing?

518
00:27:36.329 --> 00:27:38.662
Yeah.

519
00:27:42.454 --> 00:27:44.037
Did she run away?

520
00:27:46.329 --> 00:27:48.704
Was she taken?
Like that girl

521
00:27:48.787 --> 00:27:51.245
you found in the back
of the van that time?

522
00:27:52.620 --> 00:27:54.329
We're gonna bring her home.

523
00:28:00.370 --> 00:28:02.037
Hey.

524
00:28:02.120 --> 00:28:03.579
Buddy.

525
00:28:06.287 --> 00:28:08.204
I'm gonna find her. all right?

526
00:28:15.704 --> 00:28:17.620
We never would have crossed
paths with Hayley

527
00:28:17.704 --> 00:28:19.162
if you weren't
trying to sell Mom's horse.

528
00:28:22.245 --> 00:28:24.662
Almost like Mom's
trying to save her from above.

529
00:28:28.579 --> 00:28:30.620
If you won't
make it to the ceremony...

530
00:28:31.912 --> 00:28:35.495
...bringing Hayley back
is the best way to honor her.

531
00:28:51.620 --> 00:28:53.245
You know. I just got a call from

532
00:28:53.329 --> 00:28:54.954
LaChance's WITSEC agent

533
00:28:55.037 --> 00:28:58.329
thanking us for all the intel
on Sammy's contacts

534
00:28:58.412 --> 00:29:01.579
in Hawaii and California.

535
00:29:01.662 --> 00:29:03.495
What the hell is all that about?

536
00:29:03.579 --> 00:29:05.245
Just balancing the scales.

537
00:29:06.370 --> 00:29:08.870
Any idea where he's going?

538
00:29:08.954 --> 00:29:10.537
They didn't say.

539
00:29:10.620 --> 00:29:12.162
But they did assure me
it's gonna be very cold.

540
00:29:16.704 --> 00:29:18.954
Well...

541
00:29:19.037 --> 00:29:21.037
...in crappier news.

542
00:29:21.120 --> 00:29:23.495
still no hits
on the BOLO we put out.

543
00:29:23.579 --> 00:29:24.912
No luck pinging Bludsoe's phone.

544
00:29:24.995 --> 00:29:26.329
It's likely he ditched it.

545
00:29:26.412 --> 00:29:28.162
Well. he has
to advertise these girls

546
00:29:28.245 --> 00:29:29.829
in a way that we can track.

547
00:29:33.245 --> 00:29:34.579
We could catfish him.

548
00:29:34.662 --> 00:29:36.579
Set up puppet accounts.

549
00:29:36.662 --> 00:29:38.245
johns looking for girls.

550
00:29:38.329 --> 00:29:39.454
That's worth a shot.

551
00:29:39.537 --> 00:29:41.120
Where are we with
known associates?

552
00:29:41.204 --> 00:29:43.579
Got a pretty long list
of folks within the region.

553
00:29:43.662 --> 00:29:45.954
I'll send it to Kayce and Miles.

554
00:29:46.037 --> 00:29:47.579
Uh. have they
shown their faces yet?

555
00:29:47.662 --> 00:29:50.412
Gearing up to kick some doors.

556
00:29:58.454 --> 00:29:59.870
Every hour that goes by.

557
00:29:59.954 --> 00:30:01.454
chances of finding the girls
gets smaller.

558
00:30:01.537 --> 00:30:04.745
Relax.
We're making progress.

559
00:30:04.829 --> 00:30:06.329
If you're telling me
to be optimistic.

560
00:30:06.412 --> 00:30:07.787
I'm in trouble.

561
00:30:10.245 --> 00:30:12.037
What a sight for sore eyes.

562
00:30:12.120 --> 00:30:13.245
Y'all. uh. taking off

563
00:30:13.329 --> 00:30:14.412
- so soon?
- Can't find the girls

564
00:30:14.495 --> 00:30:15.579
from behind a desk.

565
00:30:15.662 --> 00:30:17.162
Shaking trees

566
00:30:17.245 --> 00:30:18.495
- is how you get the fruit.
- I appreciate y'all

567
00:30:18.579 --> 00:30:19.870
putting it on
the line for Hayley.

568
00:30:19.954 --> 00:30:22.204
just make sure
you don't cross it.

569
00:30:23.704 --> 00:30:24.870
The girls deserve
whatever it takes.

570
00:30:24.954 --> 00:30:26.370
And they deserve these predators

571
00:30:26.454 --> 00:30:28.870
go away for a long time.

572
00:30:28.954 --> 00:30:30.912
and that's why everything's
got to stick in court.

573
00:30:33.412 --> 00:30:36.162
Kayce. you just slipped
Gifford's noose.

574
00:30:37.370 --> 00:30:40.204
Miles. we know what happens
when you push things too far.

575
00:30:40.287 --> 00:30:42.412
your badge ends up
in the crosshairs.

576
00:30:47.329 --> 00:30:49.329
Thank you for taking this case.

577
00:30:51.037 --> 00:30:53.537
Hey. can't make it personal.

578
00:30:54.454 --> 00:30:56.204
Already is.

579
00:31:06.829 --> 00:31:08.745
Kurt Bludsoe's photo
just popped up

580
00:31:08.829 --> 00:31:10.620
in DMV records.
but under a different name.

581
00:31:10.704 --> 00:31:12.204
And a credit card
with that alias

582
00:31:12.287 --> 00:31:14.412
just bought gas
at a truck stop in Three Forks

583
00:31:14.495 --> 00:31:15.954
about half an hour ago.

584
00:31:16.037 --> 00:31:18.870
Three Forks?

585
00:31:18.954 --> 00:31:21.079
Kayce and Miles
are headed that way.

586
00:31:26.829 --> 00:31:28.245
I'm gonna rip Bludsoe

587
00:31:28.329 --> 00:31:29.662
from limb to limb
if we find him.

588
00:31:31.370 --> 00:31:33.412
Got to lead us
to the girls first.

589
00:31:39.495 --> 00:31:41.204
What was that.
uh. Cal was saying

590
00:31:41.287 --> 00:31:43.079
about your badge
being in the crosshairs?

591
00:31:44.995 --> 00:31:47.579
Low-level dealer
was coming onto the rez.

592
00:31:47.662 --> 00:31:49.579
spreading his poison.

593
00:31:49.662 --> 00:31:51.579
So I tracked him down.

594
00:31:51.662 --> 00:31:53.287
arrested him off tribal land.

595
00:31:55.370 --> 00:31:57.454
Cal got called in.

596
00:31:57.537 --> 00:31:59.620
Bet Rainwater loved that.

597
00:32:01.120 --> 00:32:03.704
Chairman nearly took my badge.

598
00:32:03.787 --> 00:32:06.037
Cal saw something.

599
00:32:06.120 --> 00:32:08.329
What. exactly. I don't know.

600
00:32:10.495 --> 00:32:12.120
You're a good marshal.

601
00:32:15.412 --> 00:32:18.120
Your first day
on the job. you told me

602
00:32:18.204 --> 00:32:21.162
this job might not be for me.

603
00:32:21.245 --> 00:32:23.745
If we don't get Hayley back.

604
00:32:23.829 --> 00:32:25.037
you'll be right.

605
00:32:46.745 --> 00:32:48.079
I'll look around the trucks.

606
00:32:48.162 --> 00:32:50.329
All right.
I'll take the service area.

607
00:32:50.412 --> 00:32:52.495
If you see him.
call me before you make a move.

608
00:33:20.079 --> 00:33:21.120
Hayley?

609
00:33:22.204 --> 00:33:23.412
I'm Tate's dad.

610
00:33:23.495 --> 00:33:24.537
okay?
I'm here to take you home.

611
00:33:24.620 --> 00:33:25.537
Stop. you can't talk to me.

612
00:33:25.620 --> 00:33:27.370
No. wait. wait. wait.

613
00:33:27.454 --> 00:33:28.620
I know what's happening to you.

614
00:33:28.704 --> 00:33:30.495
It's okay.

615
00:33:30.579 --> 00:33:32.412
Where's Bludsoe?

616
00:33:33.829 --> 00:33:34.870
You don't know
what he's capable of.

617
00:33:34.954 --> 00:33:35.954
He has eyes everywhere.

618
00:33:36.037 --> 00:33:37.245
I'll protect you.

619
00:33:37.329 --> 00:33:38.745
I promise.
Just come with me.

620
00:33:38.829 --> 00:33:40.870
He'll hurt the others.

621
00:33:45.870 --> 00:33:47.204
Right after
I was passed to Kurt.

622
00:33:47.287 --> 00:33:49.620
a couple other girls
tried to get away.

623
00:33:50.704 --> 00:33:52.245
He hurt them?

624
00:33:53.870 --> 00:33:55.495
Not them.

625
00:33:57.204 --> 00:33:59.662
My friend Ava.

626
00:33:59.745 --> 00:34:01.579
He killed her

627
00:34:01.662 --> 00:34:03.370
to teach us all a lesson.
I...

628
00:34:05.412 --> 00:34:06.995
The others aren't all here.

629
00:34:07.079 --> 00:34:09.120
If I go with you right now.
alone. they will pay.

630
00:34:09.204 --> 00:34:11.204
How many girls are with you?

631
00:34:12.454 --> 00:34:13.787
Nine.

632
00:34:15.829 --> 00:34:17.620
I need to stop talking to you.
Leave me alone.

633
00:34:17.704 --> 00:34:18.954
No. no. no.
If you come with me.

634
00:34:19.037 --> 00:34:20.329
I'll come back
and get the others.

635
00:34:20.412 --> 00:34:22.120
I have to go.

636
00:34:22.204 --> 00:34:24.037
You got to give me something.

637
00:34:24.120 --> 00:34:25.204
Give me something. okay?
You got to help me

638
00:34:25.287 --> 00:34:26.620
find you guys.

639
00:34:26.704 --> 00:34:28.620
I can't remember the name.

640
00:34:28.704 --> 00:34:30.204
Another stop they take us to.

641
00:34:30.287 --> 00:34:31.454
the place with the trees.
Get us there.

642
00:34:31.537 --> 00:34:32.787
Wh... Wh...

643
00:34:33.829 --> 00:34:35.495
You have to let me go.

644
00:34:52.245 --> 00:34:53.912
Like a miracle.

645
00:34:53.995 --> 00:34:56.454
Hayley falls right into
our hands and Kayce tosses her

646
00:34:56.537 --> 00:34:57.787
back to a killer.

647
00:34:57.870 --> 00:34:59.495
There were nine girls
being held.

648
00:34:59.579 --> 00:35:01.037
She didn't want
to leave them behind.

649
00:35:02.912 --> 00:35:05.037
I've seen you be real persuasive
when you need to be.

650
00:35:05.120 --> 00:35:06.620
Hey. it sounds like
the others would've been killed

651
00:35:06.704 --> 00:35:08.454
if Kayce had
forced her to go. Miles.

652
00:35:08.537 --> 00:35:10.162
Hayley's bonded

653
00:35:10.245 --> 00:35:12.162
to them.
They look out for one another.

654
00:35:13.204 --> 00:35:16.037
It's common
in extreme abuse cases.

655
00:35:16.120 --> 00:35:17.912
I'm sorry about Ava. Miles.

656
00:35:23.120 --> 00:35:24.662
If there are ten girls.

657
00:35:24.745 --> 00:35:26.704
Bludsoe has to be using a van

658
00:35:26.787 --> 00:35:29.120
or some large vehicle
to move them around.

659
00:35:30.412 --> 00:35:31.787
Hayley did say
that they were going

660
00:35:31.870 --> 00:35:33.704
to the place with all the trees.

661
00:35:34.704 --> 00:35:37.079
Anything more specific?

662
00:35:38.120 --> 00:35:39.579
No. she was scared.

663
00:35:39.662 --> 00:35:41.079
She didn't
want to be seen with me.

664
00:35:41.162 --> 00:35:43.870
Well. it's something. at least.
I'm on it.

665
00:35:43.954 --> 00:35:45.870
Skinner.
let's update that BOLO. too.

666
00:35:47.870 --> 00:35:49.412
Hey. man.

667
00:35:50.412 --> 00:35:52.204
Don't blame yourself
about Hayley.

668
00:35:52.287 --> 00:35:54.579
There was just
no easy choices there.

669
00:35:56.329 --> 00:35:58.870
Man. I prefer kicking doors
than making tough calls.

670
00:36:08.412 --> 00:36:10.120
Yeah?

671
00:36:10.204 --> 00:36:12.329
I know you have
a lot on your plate. Kayce.

672
00:36:12.412 --> 00:36:15.954
but Mo shared that you
and Miles have made progress.

673
00:36:16.037 --> 00:36:17.579
but didn't say what kind.

674
00:36:17.662 --> 00:36:19.620
We're doing everything we can.

675
00:36:19.704 --> 00:36:23.079
Well. despite knowing
how these things usually end.

676
00:36:23.162 --> 00:36:25.245
I confess. hope is contagious.

677
00:36:27.120 --> 00:36:29.329
Well. the last thing I want
to do is cause you to lose it.

678
00:36:29.412 --> 00:36:30.662
I swallowed my pride

679
00:36:30.745 --> 00:36:32.495
asking the marshals
for help earlier.

680
00:36:32.579 --> 00:36:35.745
I did so knowing
you'd be leading the charge.

681
00:36:37.037 --> 00:36:38.787
I'm doing my best.

682
00:36:38.870 --> 00:36:41.370
Well. your best is what
Hayley and Ava deserve.

683
00:36:41.454 --> 00:36:43.704
And I know
you're their best hope.

684
00:36:46.912 --> 00:36:48.829
Well. I'll
keep you updated. sir.

685
00:37:02.745 --> 00:37:04.287
Where's Kayce?

686
00:37:04.370 --> 00:37:06.912
Send him out to aid and abet
any other criminals?

687
00:37:06.995 --> 00:37:09.162
What'd I say about
taking this so personally?

688
00:37:09.245 --> 00:37:12.870
I need you to throttle down.
okay? Look.

689
00:37:12.954 --> 00:37:14.412
we got a trail
on the breadcrumbs

690
00:37:14.495 --> 00:37:16.162
that Hayley dropped for Kayce.

691
00:37:16.245 --> 00:37:17.662
What kind of breadcrumbs?

692
00:37:17.745 --> 00:37:19.745
The place with the trees
isn't about actual trees.

693
00:37:19.829 --> 00:37:21.454
It's a logo.

694
00:37:21.537 --> 00:37:24.537
Ponderosa Truck Stops
all across I-90. There is one

695
00:37:24.620 --> 00:37:27.704
50 miles
from where Kayce saw Hayley.

696
00:37:28.745 --> 00:37:31.162
Camper's how
Bludsoe's moving them.

697
00:37:31.245 --> 00:37:33.162
Two other guys must be
Bludsoe's eyes and muscle.

698
00:37:34.370 --> 00:37:35.495
When was this?

699
00:37:35.579 --> 00:37:36.870
Are they still there?

700
00:37:36.954 --> 00:37:39.912
First one is three hours ago.

701
00:37:39.995 --> 00:37:42.787
This one's 40 minutes ago.

702
00:37:42.870 --> 00:37:44.829
- So we've lost them.
- Yeah. but

703
00:37:44.912 --> 00:37:46.495
not if we can track the camper.

704
00:37:46.579 --> 00:37:48.537
As long as they
stay on public highways.

705
00:37:48.620 --> 00:37:50.204
I can use OCR to find them.

706
00:37:50.287 --> 00:37:52.370
Kayce's gamble paid off.

707
00:37:52.454 --> 00:37:54.037
Not until we find the girls.

708
00:37:54.120 --> 00:37:57.245
Road weather camera just
got a hit on the camper moving

709
00:37:57.329 --> 00:37:59.120
south on 287 near Toston.

710
00:37:59.204 --> 00:38:01.787
We cut across 84. might be able
to take them down by Norris.

711
00:38:01.870 --> 00:38:03.537
Go.
Hey. we're rolling out.

712
00:38:16.162 --> 00:38:17.954
We should be closing in on them.

713
00:38:18.037 --> 00:38:20.287
Are there any state troopers
or local police in the area?

714
00:38:20.370 --> 00:38:22.454
We're the closest out.

715
00:38:24.620 --> 00:38:26.537
Could be your
redemption. cowboy.

716
00:38:27.579 --> 00:38:29.037
Better not miss.

717
00:38:40.204 --> 00:38:41.787
Okay. I've got eyes
on the target.

718
00:38:41.870 --> 00:38:43.620
We moving in heavy?

719
00:38:43.704 --> 00:38:45.912
Negative.
We're gonna hold back.

720
00:38:45.995 --> 00:38:49.120
keep eyes on them.
When they stop. we'll pounce.

721
00:38:49.204 --> 00:38:51.204
There's a small town
about ten miles ahead.

722
00:38:51.287 --> 00:38:52.787
They could stop there.

723
00:38:56.537 --> 00:38:58.745
Low vis. Miles.
Low vis. hold back.

724
00:39:00.245 --> 00:39:01.370
Low vis. hold back.

725
00:39:01.454 --> 00:39:03.412
- Hold back.
- Miles.

726
00:39:03.495 --> 00:39:05.204
we have to take them
with their guard down.

727
00:39:08.204 --> 00:39:10.537
They're accelerating.
They-they've spotted us.

728
00:39:10.620 --> 00:39:13.662
Girls are at risk
if we don't back off.

729
00:39:13.745 --> 00:39:15.454
Back off.
we'll never see 'em again.

730
00:39:16.829 --> 00:39:18.412
What's the call?

731
00:39:21.370 --> 00:39:22.662
If we get ahead.

732
00:39:22.745 --> 00:39:24.245
we can lay down a spike strip.

733
00:39:24.329 --> 00:39:25.662
bring 'em to a halt.

734
00:39:25.745 --> 00:39:27.954
Copy.
We'll handle it. Okay.

735
00:39:28.037 --> 00:39:30.120
you're gonna get ahead of 'em.
all right?

736
00:39:33.912 --> 00:39:35.162
Okay. look out. Gun.

737
00:39:35.245 --> 00:39:36.245
Pull back. pull back.

738
00:39:36.329 --> 00:39:37.912
Pull back.

739
00:39:37.995 --> 00:39:39.829
Shots fired! Shots fired!

740
00:39:39.912 --> 00:39:41.620
I can't return fire
with the girls in there.

741
00:39:43.245 --> 00:39:44.537
Suggestion box is open.

742
00:39:44.620 --> 00:39:47.204
I'll draw fire
so you can overtake 'em.

743
00:39:47.287 --> 00:39:48.662
Good copy.

744
00:39:48.745 --> 00:39:51.162
The shooter pops up.
put his head down.

745
00:39:51.245 --> 00:39:53.454
I can't shoot him
with the girls in there.

746
00:39:53.537 --> 00:39:55.537
Improvise.

747
00:40:11.287 --> 00:40:13.120
Punch it.

748
00:40:14.662 --> 00:40:15.870
Go. go. go. go. go. go. go.

749
00:40:31.329 --> 00:40:33.537
Go. go. go. go. go. go. go.

750
00:40:42.745 --> 00:40:43.912
Not gonna get far.

751
00:40:51.329 --> 00:40:52.954
Okay. y'all take the
back door. We're gonna go around

752
00:40:53.037 --> 00:40:55.204
and get the driver.

753
00:41:11.704 --> 00:41:13.204
Clear.
Secure the girls.

754
00:41:19.079 --> 00:41:21.954
Kayce. sitrep.

755
00:41:23.037 --> 00:41:24.537
We missed them.

756
00:41:24.620 --> 00:41:26.412
They're gone.
